[ 33444] By: nicholas				   on 2008/03/05  15:30:36
	Log: Integrate:
	     [ 33443]
	     Integrate:
	     [ 33437]
	     Three variables in S_scan_trans only hold flags for op_private, so can
	     be U8.
     Branch: maint-5.8/perl
	  !> toke.c
