[ 32417] By: nicholas				   on 2007/11/20  13:39:23
	Log: Integrate:
	     [ 31301]
	     Subject: Re: localising hash element by variable
	     From: Bo Lindbergh <blgl@hagernas.com>
	     Date: Mon, 28 May 2007 20:26:00 +0200
	     Message-Id: <BC2C451F-B286-4D38-923E-E3B473F7B5E1@hagernas.com>
	     
