[ 32371] By: nicholas				   on 2007/11/17  16:19:24
	Log: Integrate:
	     [ 31398]
	     Subject: [PATCH] Test::Builder tickles Pod::Html parsing stupidity bug
	     From: demerphq <demerphq@gmail.com>
