[ 32295] By: nicholas				   on 2007/11/12  22:22:11
	Log: Integrate:
	     [ 31702]
	     Use sysconf/getpagesize/page.h to determine page size on Linux,
	     in that order.
	     
	     Subject: Re: [PATCH] Various Gentoo Patches
