[ 30703] By: nicholas				   on 2007/03/22  23:14:35
	Log: Integrate:
	     [ 30345]
	     newHV doesn't need to turn off POK or NOK, as they will default to not
	     being set.
	     
	     [ 30659]
	     Don't try to set the NV on a typeglob-in-action. Should cure bug
	     41920.
     Branch: maint-5.8/perl
	  !> hv.c sv.c
