[ 30623] By: nicholas				   on 2007/03/18  23:08:11
	Log: Integrate the regexp.t changes from:
	     [ 28816]
	     Subject: [PATCH] Teach regex optimiser how to handle (?=) and (?<=) properly.
	     From: demerphq <demerphq@gmail.com>
