	     From: Bo Lindbergh <blgl@hagernas.com>
	     Date: Sat, 9 Dec 2006 12:17:53 +0100
	     Message-Id: <A4BDE74B-DB3A-41C0-B2BE-FCEE0E15AB54@hagernas.com>
	     
