[ 30244] By: nicholas				   on 2007/02/12  21:35:09
	Log: Integrate:
	     [ 27939]
	     Subject: Update to AUTHORS file
	     From: Joshua Rodd <joshua@rodd.us>
	     Date: Sat, 22 Apr 2006 14:39:11 -0400
	     Message-ID: <20060422183911.GA19435@rodd.us>
	     
	     [ 28102]
